description: Come seek this elegant truck in green if you’re craving authentic and delicious Japanese and Hawaiian cuisine.Dawn Kado was introduced to her love for cooking through the post-war Japanese-American and Hawaiian recipes that she grew up with. Delightful dishes such as Chicken & Beef Teriyaki, Japanese-style Ribs, and Spam Musubi helped to shape Dawn’s culinary pursuits and now she’s sharing the love with Sacramento. Everyone is certainly feeling the thrill, tasting this amazing food from Kado’s Asian Grill.
name: Kado's Asian Grill
